{"tid":54132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"諗深一層 其實一路都玩緊自己","createTime":"2016-12-25T09:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T11:52:14.000Z","uid":15195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e16ea37c7b72dc1eaca74b6715ad50a06d05f189","tid":54132,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"中學畢業後至開始拍拖<br />\n但唔知點解識親都係中學生<br />\n每次都係佢地出黎返工就散<br />\n其實我冇得怪佢地<br />\n對佢地黎講 未離開校園<br />\n唔知出面有更多選擇<br />\n步入社會先發覺<br />\n原來比起佢地自己一直想像既<br />\n美好 更多選擇<br />\n有其他更加風趣 善於同佢地溝通既人<br />\n可以照顧佢地 或者 發覺原來我根本唔啱佢地<br />\n我自己都應該注意 根本唔應該去接觸佢地<br />\n因為根本唔同世界<br />\n祝佢地快樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝全天下派帽俾人既八婆<br />\n全天下俾帽人戴既厹含家剷<br />\n日日俾狗屌 俾車撞到殘廢<br />\n長命百歲 百病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e11a7a4bba7348893e567e1d367f8d1bd19be7","tid":54132,"uid":14004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"你食親都係學生妹<br />\n幾多高登仔恨都恨唔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abde4678ed82e85c1427bd50a357832d8317c17a","tid":54132,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你食親都係學生妹<br />\n幾多高登仔恨都恨唔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解次次都咁既收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}